The paper deals with visual depiction and feature extraction, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper involves the analysis of spatial and chromatic histograms, which are commonly used in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the expansion of the capability of a visual feature, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
